508ce68c0ce","tid":2270673,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T02:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cspinet.org/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/RiskyMeat_FB.jpg?itok=0ABDlZ7I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcspinet.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Flarge%2Fpublic%2FRiskyMeat_FB.jpg%3Fitok%3D0ABDlZ7I&h=3bd52841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最危險既肉類其實係雞同免治牛肉<br />\n沙門氏菌同O-157大腸桿菌所殺既人<br />\n遠遠多過豬絛蟲"},{"pid":"c06ff0241bd75fe7fcdcfa956a90cdf24d94d41b","tid":2270673,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"674a9c803e4419ac9e87015b73e79508ce68c0ce","tid":2270673,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T02:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cspinet.org/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/RiskyMeat_FB.jpg?itok=0ABDlZ7I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcspinet.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Flarge%2Fpublic%2FRiskyMeat_FB.jpg%3Fitok%3D0ABDlZ7I&h=3bd52841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最危險既肉類其實係雞同免治牛肉<br />\n沙門氏菌同O-157大腸桿菌所殺既人<br />\n遠遠多過豬絛蟲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:42:32.000Z","msg":"what&rsquo;s the risk"},{"pid":"a0f5025fdd985bae79e27389e602480bbc17f4f1","tid":2270673,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d37ed296374f96fdc88e4a12aeda0f8b1fd0602","tid":2270673,"uid":248187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7b704f7a6d394961df197313dea8d30649353cb","tid":2270673,"uid":121126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T01:27:28.000Z","msg":"因為牛羊既寄生蟲只會留係腸道，但豬既寄生蟲可以穿過腸去到全身肌肉同大腦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T01:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"豬帶絛蟲"},{"pid":"51bb1f656673cfe85f128f102b8dcd70fa61bd54","tid":2270673,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c06ff0241bd75fe7fcdcfa956a90cdf24d94d41b","tid":2270673,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"674a9c803e4419ac9e87015b73e79508ce68c0ce","tid":2270673,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T02:08:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cspinet.org/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/RiskyMeat_FB.jpg?itok=0ABDlZ7I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcspinet.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Flarge%2Fpublic%2FRiskyMeat_FB.jpg%3Fitok%3D0ABDlZ7I&h=3bd52841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最危險既肉類其實係雞同免治牛肉<br />\n沙門氏菌同O-157大腸桿菌所殺既人<br />\n遠遠多過豬絛蟲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T03:42:32.000Z","msg":"what&rsquo;s the risk"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T04:02:26.000Z","msg":"現代化既養殖場出產既肉已經好少有寄生蟲<br />\n無論豬牛羊雞鴨鵝都係<br />\n不過雞肌肉密度唔高<br />\n屠宰時腸道入面既細菌好似沙門氏菌好容易就滲入肉入面<br />\n所以一定要well done<br />\n而高致病性既O-157大腸桿菌普遍存在係草食性動物度<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">豬係有不過比例上少好多</span><br />\n雖然肉既密度高菌只會依附係肉表面<br />\n不過攪碎後就唔同咁講喇<br />\n碎咗後表面面積幾何級數上升<br />\n食來源唔可靠既半生熟漢堡根本同玩俄羅斯方塊冇咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}